---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Build Instructions

### 1. Install Dependencies
```bash
npm install
```

### 2. Build SCSS
```bash
npm run build
```

### 3. Watch for Changes
```bash
npm run watch
```

Make sure your Sass files compile into `dist/style.css` correctly.

---

## â™¿ Accessibility

This project is built to meet [WCAG 2.1 A and AA](https://www.w3.org/WAI/WCAG21/quickref/) standards:

- Keyboard navigable
- Skip to content link
- Semantic headings and landmark roles
- Sufficient color contrast and alt text
- No keyboard traps

---

## ğŸš€ Deployment

To deploy to GitHub Pages:

1. Push to your GitHub repo
2. Go to Settings > Pages
3. Set source to your root or `/docs` folder
4. Ensure `index.html` and `dist/style.css` are committed

